{"tid":502591,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"跌親發高燒入院Jeana屁股含膿","createTime":"2017-12-18T05:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T09:43:26.000Z","uid":47132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"718b365f241ce1120500e8f7dd15386a665d9f46","tid":502591,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171218/large/18ec4p2newe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171218%2Flarge%2F18ec4p2newe.jpg&h=f626c0c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何佩瑜（Jeana）今年3月在台灣發生撞車意外送院，前日又因之前在家中跌傷入院留醫，應驗了禍不單行。<br />\nJeana前晚於社交網貼出留院的打吊針相，並留言：「想不到這麼簡單一跌，竟然要這樣子。」昨早她再貼出一張女子背影圖後再留言：「一臉擔心的媽媽，辛苦了。」記者昨致電Jeana，她氣若游絲回覆：「我兩周前喺屋企沖涼跣親，唔覺意跌親pat pat，佢又痛又腫，我以為捽吓冇事，點知越嚟越腫，又越嚟越痛，我呢幾日仲發高燒，成40度唔退，噚日去咗睇醫生，醫生要我立即入院，打抗生素針，因為我pat pat個傷口發炎，腫到成個芒果咁，今朝要做手術放膿，手術完咗，醫生話要留院幾日先可以出院。」"},{"pid":"780ae223d659d32eb4acfd7822c00e0aae979346","tid":502591,"uid":38194,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:14:15.000Z","msg":"肛交累事"},{"pid":"db6806c57942afcfe8656bedb34cee956d4d3b66","tid":502591,"uid":126766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:18:36.000Z","msg":"jeana<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6592675a346c59a391c57e414ade6d1a5e029ed0","tid":502591,"uid":144843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2080a99616a67eb79d7e9e6940a9ffddb186e9f8","tid":502591,"uid":21028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"跌親可以發炎到咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893124a3d4ff3ed2842c8db9cadbb4fa5c465cff","tid":502591,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0